    "summary": "I hold 20 years of HR experience in leading Global People functions. Now scaling Canonical, Open Source Technology, having reached the mark of 1000 people located remotely in more than 70 countries, and previously at Irdeto, Cyber Security Tech. I held HR- and Business Partner roles for a broad range of commercial, technical and corporate departments across the globe at Mattel Toys (Barbie, Scrabble, Hot Wheels, FisherPrice and more). I have a wide experience in the field of Human Resources in a fast-paced and dynamic environment and high-performing culture. As a Generalist at heart, my passion is all about cross-pollination, to generate a holistic approach to HR, being guided by transparency, fairness and high quality. I have experience in Org Design and Change-Management, Performance Management, Coaching, Talent Development, Training Delivery, Relocations/Mobility, Remote-first, Job-Architecture, Benefits, Recruitment and Selection, Engagement, Cultural Transformation, Employment Value Proposition and M&A's and hold a Master degree in Work-, Organizational & Clinical Psychology with additional specialization in Labour Law, Strategy and Supervisory Boards. I am German and lived in Australia and South Africa, now in The Netherlands. ",
